title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Photographic Or Cinematographic Products
description: Imports Intra Eu - Photographic Or Cinematographic Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 11.29 GBP Million in September from 12.20 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Photographic Or Cinematographic in the United Kingdom averaged 27.17 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 59.57 GBP Million in June of 2001 and a record low of 6.60 GBP Million in May of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Photographic Or Cinematogra.
